data.description: MOVE IN READY! This two-story, stucco home comes with all appliances! Large Master Bedroom with tray ceiling and walk-in closet. Master Bathroom with walk-in shower and Garden Tub. Half bathroom and laundry room located downstairs. Stainless Steel kitchen appliances. Kitchen with eat-in area and breakfast bar. Pond view with covered back patio. New AC system. Home is minutes away from amenities. Perfect location - 15 minutes away from Atlantic Beach and JTB. BONUS: home also equipped with Tesla plug-in. Schedule your showing today!
